一款由[[Omgpop|Omgpop]]開發的[[流動軟體應用程式|流動軟件遊戲]]。在遊戲中，兩名玩家需要輪流繪畫方案內容及猜測方的身份，而繪畫方的目的就是讓猜測方猜對圖畫所表達的詞語。<ref name="official"/>

== 遊戲系統 ==
在《你畫我猜》中，兩名玩家輪流交替繪畫方和猜測方的身份。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ign.com/games/draw-something/iphone-129372 |title=Draw Something - IGN |accessdate=2013-09-23 |archive-date=2017-03-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170324115815/http://www.ign.com/games/draw-something/iphone-129372 |dead-url=no }}</ref>遊戲開始時，繪畫方會得到隨機的英文詞語，並且需要將之繪畫出來。而猜測方則需要猜測圖畫所表達的詞。每當猜測方成功猜測一個詞時，繪畫方就能獲得1至3枚金幣。<ref name="official"/>

當繪畫方完成繪畫後，猜測方能夠選擇回放繪畫方的繪畫，但其間不能暫停。猜測方亦能看見數個空格，而空格的數量代表詞語的字數。猜測方亦會得到一堆字母方格，猜測方需要從中選出詞語中有的字母。猜測方能夠不停地猜測，並且沒有時間限制。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://gigaom.com/2012/03/16/dont-call-it-a-game-how-draw-something-hit-30-million-downloads/ |title=Don’t call it a game: How Draw Something hit 30 million downloads |accessdate=2013-09-23 |archive-date=2020-08-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200803160939/https://gigaom.com/2012/03/16/dont-call-it-a-game-how-draw-something-hit-30-million-downloads/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

玩家得到的金幣能夠用來購買更多種顏色，讓猜測方更易明白繪畫方的繪畫。金幣亦於能用來購買「炸彈」。這些金幣能夠用錢來購買。<ref name="official">{{Cite web |url=http://omgpop.com/drawsomething |title=Drawing with friends goes mobile. |accessdate=2013-09-23 |archive-date=2012-03-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120322062502/http://omgpop.com/drawsomething |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 工具 ==
每個玩家均能獲得一定數量的「炸彈」。作為猜測方，那些炸彈能夠為猜測方消除一個字母方格或顯示詞語中的一個字。作為繪畫方，那些炸彈能夠讓玩家重新選擇一個詞語。若玩家用光了炸彈而又無法猜出那個字，那麼玩家就只能棄權。若玩家棄權的話，那麼兩人的連勝紀錄就會重設。透過棄權，玩家能獲得新詞語。<ref name="official"/>

== 發展 ==
《你畫我猜》善用了[[Facebook|Facebook]]用戶的高速增長來擴張遊戲市場。當玩家透過Facebook用戶進行遊戲時，玩家就能和其友人進行遊戲。玩家只需按下友人的Facebook用戶名稱，就能和其友人進行遊戲。若玩家想邀請沒有玩此遊戲的友人參加，他們亦能在遊戲中這樣做。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ign.com/wikis/draw-something/Bombs |title=Draw Something - IGN guide |accessdate=2013-09-23 |archive-date=2019-06-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190608142807/https://www.ign.com/wikis/draw-something/Bombs |dead-url=no }}</ref>

一個近期的更新允許玩家保存和分享他們的畫作。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.wpcentral.com/draw-something-updated-make-it-more-stable |title=Draw Something updated to make it more stable? |accessdate=2013-09-23 |archive-date=2013-02-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130208060503/http://www.wpcentral.com/draw-something-updated-make-it-more-stable |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==反響==
此遊戲獲得一致好評。[[GameZebo|GameZebo]]給予此遊戲4/5分，並指出「《你畫我猜》已經超越了社交遊戲，它是一個進入我們思想的窗口」。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.gamezebo.com/games/draw-something/review |title=Draw Something - GameZebo |accessdate=2013-09-23 |archive-date=2013-05-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130512011019/http://www.gamezebo.com/games/draw-something/review |dead-url=no }}</ref>[[Touch_Arcade|Touch Arcade]]給予此遊戲5/5分，並指出「每個人都應該下載這個遊戲」。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://toucharcade.com/2012/03/20/draw-something-gets-retina-ipad-update-but-everyone-should-download-this-game/ |title=Draw Something - Touch Arcade |accessdate=2013-09-23 |archive-date=2020-02-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200207114659/https://toucharcade.com/2012/03/20/draw-something-gets-retina-ipad-update-but-everyone-should-download-this-game/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>而[[Pocket_Gamer|Pocket Gamer]]則給予此遊戲9/10分，並授予此遊戲「金獎」。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.pocketgamer.co.uk/r/Multiformat/Draw+Something/review.asp?c=38998 |title=Draw Something - Pocket Gamer |accessdate=2013-09-23 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304112528/http://www.pocketgamer.co.uk/r/Multiformat/Draw+Something/review.asp?c=38998 |dead-url=no }}</ref>此遊戲亦獲頒2012年亂舞應用程式聚光燈獎（Flurry App Spotlight Award）。<ref>{{cite news|title=Red Stamp, Fooducate and Draw Something Win Flurry 2012 App Spotlight Awards|url=http://www.bradenton.com/2012/03/14/3938013/red-stamp-fooducate-and-draw-something.html|accessdate=14 March 2012|newspaper=[[Bradenton_Herald|Bradenton Herald]]|date=14 March 2012|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120324100933/http://www.bradenton.com/2012/03/14/3938013/red-stamp-fooducate-and-draw-something.html|archivedate=2012年3月24日}}</ref>

此遊戲非常受玩家歡迎。在發佈五週後，此遊戲已累積逾2000萬次下載。<ref>{{cite web|title=Draw Something app surges to 20 million downloads|url=http://www.t3.com/news/draw-something-app-surges-to-20-million-downloads-1|publisher=[[T3_(magazine)|T3 magazine]]|accessdate=14 March 2012|archive-date=2019-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190629054421/https://www.t3.com/news/draw-something-app-surges-to-20-million-downloads-1|dead-url=no}}</ref>在發佈50天後，此遊戲累積逾5000萬次下載。<ref>{{cite news|title=Draw Something is 'fastest growing' mobile game|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/technology-17624172|accessdate=7 April 2012|newspaper=BBC|date=5 April 2012|archive-date=2020-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111231331/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/technology-17624172|dead-url=no}}</ref>隨著遊戲的增長，此遊戲引來了其他遊戲公司的青睞。於2012年3月，[[Zynga|Zynga]]以1.8億美元收購《你畫我猜》和Omgpop。 <ref>{{cite news|title=A Game Explodes and Changes Life Overnight at a Struggling Start-Up|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2012/03/26/technology/draw-something-changes-the-game-quickly-for-omgpop.html?_r=1|newspaper=New York Times|date=March 25, 2012|accessdate=2013-09-23|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112033741/http://www.nytimes.com/2012/03/26/technology/draw-something-changes-the-game-quickly-for-omgpop.html?_r=1|dead-url=no}}</ref>但是，在Zynga在收購《你畫我猜》1個月後，此遊戲的每日用戶減少了500萬。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/2012-05-02-draw-something-in-rapid-decline-for-daily-users-count |title=Draw Something loses 5 million daily users in one month |accessdate=2013-09-23 |archive-date=2019-06-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190616213941/https://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/2012-05-02-draw-something-in-rapid-decline-for-daily-users-count |dead-url=no }}</ref>儘管如此，在發佈1年後，此遊戲的下載次數仍然超越了1億次。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.joystiq.com/2013/02/19/draw-something-crests-100-million-downloads-after-one-year/ |title=Draw Something crests 100 million downloads after one year - joystiq |access-date=2013-09-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130424134432/http://www.joystiq.com/2013/02/19/draw-something-crests-100-million-downloads-after-one-year/ |archive-date=2013-04-24 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

2013年4月25日，《[[你畫我猜2|你畫我猜2]]》於[[iOS|iOS]]上發佈。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://draw2.zynga.com/draw2 |title=Draw Something 2 |accessdate=2013-09-23 |archive-date=2013-10-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131004103253/http://draw2.zynga.com/draw2 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 棋盤遊戲 ==
於2012年，Zynga與[[孩之寶|孩之寶]]合作推出了一款名為《孩之寶遊戲》（Hasbro Gaming）的棋盤遊戲。該遊戲係改編自《你畫我猜》。該遊戲是Zynga推出的數個棋盤遊戲中的其中一個。其他Zynga推出的棋盤遊戲包括填字游戏《[[Words_with_Friends|Words with Friends]]》、《城市小鎮》（CityVille）版本《[[地產大亨|地產大亨]]》和幾種改編自《[[FarmVille|FarmVille]]》的兒童遊戲。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.hasbrotoyshop.com/zynga |title=Zynga games page of HasbroToyShop.com. Retrieved October 17, 2012 |publisher=Hasbrotoyshop.com |date= |accessdate=2013-01-28 |archive-date=2014-10-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141025152446/http://www.hasbrotoyshop.com/zynga |dead-url=no }}</ref>

